Package Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Boss
    Boss object in Mats platform worlds, he moves around and shoots bullets at Mats trying to kill him The boss is killed when Mats his hitpoins run out
    BossBullet
    The bullets the boss shoots at Mat, if Mat collides with a bullet he dies
    Bullet
    Abstract bullet class
    Enemy
    Enemy object in Mats world, if math collides with them he dies They move around in the game, either vertically of horizontally Mat can shoot at them to kill them
    EnemyObject
    Abstract enemyObject class the enemies in the game can extend from
    Game
    The Game object
    GameObject
    Abstract class every moving object inherits from
    Level
    This is the level object creating the layout for the different types of enemies/ platforms and where to place them
    LevelData  
    Main
    Main class for Mat in the plat.
    Player
    The player object in the game controlled by the player
    PlayerBullet
    The bulletclass to the playerbullets
    Spikes
    Spikes that Mat can move on
